name: A Typical Day Of A King
description: Gosho, a self-proclaimed king of the tropics, enjoys spending his time watching TV all day as he is always wearing his best drip. His favorite motto is: "Better to be late than to arrive ugly" He is also looking for a girlfriend! This art piece comes with a special NFT #5 from Vegzi's Hiragana Collection. Medium: 1080x1080 MP4 without sound / Animated illustration loop / Artist: Vegzi / Twitter: @Vegzi1 / Created and minted: 22nd of June 2021
